Introduction

HIGHCOLOR (Korean: 하이컬러; Japanese: ハイカラー) was a Korean pop/Korean R&B female duo under Million Market. They formerly were set to debut as a 4-member girl group in 2018 under Mostable Music but the debut was cancelled. In February 26, 2019 they debuted as a duo.
